        <item>
            <title>YouTube Premium 跨區「印度人」新解約潮，之前都無事但今日大量網友中招</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/youtube-premium-5/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=youtube-premium-5</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/youtube-premium-5/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:58:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[應用軟件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[youtube]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[youtube premium]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273518</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">YouTube 疑似再次收緊 Premium 會籍費用政策，若使用土耳其、印度版本的 YouTube Premium，YouTube 已出電郵通知用户要使用印度境內的付款方式。有網民在社交平台上發文，指自己今日開始已用不到  YouTube Premium。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273519 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462537122_8674094289-438x580.jpg" alt="" width="438" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462537122_8674094289-438x580.jpg 438w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462537122_8674094289.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 438px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲若使用印度版本的 YouTube Premium，12 月 5 日前需將付款方式更新為印度境內付款方式</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">YouTube 向用户發送電郵，指「印度的 YouTube Premium 會籍費用須使用印度境內的付款方式支付。」若想保留會藉，必須在 2024 年 12 月 5 日前將付款方式更新為印度境內的付款方式。網民在 LIHKG 表示「收到 email 要一個月內 update 做印度信用卡」。有網民回覆指不只印度，好多土耳其用户亦收到通知要更改付款資料。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273555 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592-621x580.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592-621x580.jpg 621w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592.jpg 963w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 621px" /></a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273524 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-694x544.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="544" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-694x544.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1.jpg 1149w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲網民在 LIHKG 表示「收到 email 要一個月內 update 做印度信用卡」（圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273526 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x169.png" alt="" width="694" height="169" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x169.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1280x311.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_.png 1292w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲網民笑指「打緊杖呀點去銀行出卡」（圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">其他網民就表示不如直接使用 AD Block，亦有網民建議直接使用香港版本 YouTube Premium，並取笑「封得你遲啦」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273521 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_.jpg 756w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲其他網民就表示不如直接使用 AD Block（圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273527 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-1-694x180.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="180" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-1-694x180.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-1.jpg 1218w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民取笑「封得你遲啦」（圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>、Youtube</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
