        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【評測】vivo X200 Pro mini 國行開箱評測，機仔細細易外攜 + 單手握機操控手感佳 + 高屏佔比熒幕表現出色 + 相機夜攝較遜色 + 旗艦效能電量超長氣</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/vivo-x200promini-chinaversion-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vivo-x200promini-chinaversion-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/vivo-x200promini-chinaversion-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 14:33:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vivo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200 Pro mini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273011</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前筆者就已為大家評測過 vivo 剛推出的國行版本 X200 Pro，但其實同場發佈有另一部筆者覺得更吸引的新機，就是屬於機仔細細但同樣是旗艦效能配置的 X200 Pro mini。究竟這部「細細粒」表現上是否可以媲美「大阿哥」X200 Pro？就讓 Edward 為 unwire.hk 讀者們來個詳細開箱評測吧。</p><h2>vivo X200 Pro mini 開箱直擊</h2><p>在為大家分享 vivo X200 Pro mini 的使用體驗前，同樣地先讓 Edward 為大家來個開箱直擊吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04639-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04639-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04639.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是 vivo X200 Pro mini 的包裝盒，大家可以見到它與「大哥」X200 Pro 的包裝盒設計一模一樣，不過明顯比較細一點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04641-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04641-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04641.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者借測的是鈦青版，配置為 16GB RAM + 512GB 內存。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273086" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04643-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04643-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04643.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打開包裝盒，就已經見到 X200 Pro mini 的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04644.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而底層就會見到所有 X200 Pro mini 附送的配件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273088" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04646-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04646-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04646.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大家可以見到 X200 Pro mini 除了附送透明手機殼外，亦設有 SIM 卡槽針、充電火牛及 USB-A to USB-C 數據電源線。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273089" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04650-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04650-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04650.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273090" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04651-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04651-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04651.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273091" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04654-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04654-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04654.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最後撕走手機上的包裝紙，再長按開關鍵，就可以開啟手機電源並進行初設始定了，至此開箱部分完畢。</p><h2>設計與「大機」相若但細機更好揸手</h2><p>先説設計上吧，今次 vivo 推出的「細屏旗艦」X200 Pro mini，在機身設計上基本上與「大機」X200 Pro 有 8 成相似，機背同樣採用加入磨砂工藝的玻璃物料，機邊依然採用較厚身平面的邊框，只是機面機底邊位取走了弧位，改為採用直角設計，令 Pro mini 感覺上就像一部擁有四圓角的「磚頭」。不過由於它的機身大細比「大機」細得多，體積只有「大機」的 84% 左右，厚度亦比舊機更薄，只有 8.15mm，重量更只有 187g，加上依然採用超幼邊框及超高屏佔比的熒幕，令「機仔細細」的 X200 Pro mini 不但外攜時更加方便放入褲袋或褸袋，長時間單手握機拿在手上使用亦更加舒服，單手握機打字亦自然沒有問題。而且它機身較細較薄較輕，在「大機」出現的頭重尾輕問題在 X200 Pro mini 上似乎不太感覺得到，亦令使用手感比「大機」更理想。值得一提的是，雖然機身設計與「大機」相若，但 Pro mini 的配色，除了黑、白兩個較大路的款式外，另外兩款配色「鈦青」及「微粉」就屬於較具活力、較清新的配色，相對「大機」的「寶石藍」及「鈦色」，相信更能吸引後生仔入手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273093" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04697-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04697-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04697.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 Pro mini 在設計上，基本上與「大哥」X200 Pro 有 8 成相似，最大分別就是機身明顯細了一個圈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04675-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04675-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04675.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲究竟 X200 Pro mini 機身有幾「細」？筆者拿來同樣是細機旗艦的 iPhone 13 Pro 比一比，大家可以見到 X200 Pro mini 也只是比 iPhone 13 Pro 大一點點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273096" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04679-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04679-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04679.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273097" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04668-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04668-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04668.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一個 X200 Pro mini 與 X200 Pro 最大的機身設計分別，就是前者採用的是機面機底邊位均是全平的設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04665-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04665-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04665.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而機側邊框依然採用金屬物料製造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273099" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04662-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04662-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04662.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於機背，就依然用上加入了磨砂工藝的強化玻璃物料，而今次筆者借測的鈦青色，確實十分耐看。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273106" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04702-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04702-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04702.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於機邊，由於採用平面設計，加上機身不算大，所以握機時完全沒有界手感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04708-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04708-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04708.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04705-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04705-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04705.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04710-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04710-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04710.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外筆者以電子磅量度過，X200 Pro mini 機身重量只是 191.4g，以旗艦手機來説算是頗輕身，外攜使用十分方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273101" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04700-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04700-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04700.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04699-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04699-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04699.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04701-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04701-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04701.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273104" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04703-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04703-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04703.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲由於機身細又薄，而且頗輕身，所以即使長時間單手握機操控或打字，手感依然十分舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04676-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04676-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04676.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，它同樣內建了熒幕下指紋解鎖功能，不過大家要留意的是，它只是一般的屏下指紋模組，而非像 X200 Pro 般採用超聲波熒幕下指紋辨識技術，所以如果用家手指濕，在 X200 Pro mini 上是不能解鎖的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04666-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04666-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04666.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04667-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04667-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04667.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於機身配置方面，音量鍵及開關鍵設於機身右側，而內置喇叭、USB-C 插槽及 SIM 卡槽就位於機底。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273113 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-13-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-13-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-13.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273114 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-14-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-14-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-14.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273115 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-15-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-15-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-15.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273116 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-16-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-16-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-16.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲介面方面，X200 Pro mini 內建了 OriginOS 5，設計上與其他採用相同 OS 的 vivo 國行手機相比如出一轍。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273117 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241101_-2-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241101_-2-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241101_-2.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273118 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-17-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-17-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-17.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 Pro mini 國行同樣內建了 Google 框架，所以只需要在官方商店下載並安裝 Google Play Store，登入後就可如港行般下載及安裝軟件或遊戲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04714-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04714-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04714.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04715-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04715-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04715.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者實測過可以完美使用 Google Play Store 之餘，亦可安裝及使用各種 GMS 服務。</p><br /><b>
]]>
